{"tid":1115694,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"明年 3 月發表 IPhone 8s 搶中階市場","createTime":"2019-04-19T11:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T17:07:39.000Z","uid":50534,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"24996fa73d3c2fc9314ce29e9c5bd463ad6085ce","tid":1115694,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/04/19/apple-launch-new-4-7-inch-iphone-8-2020/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F19%2Fapple-launch-new-4-7-inch-iphone-8-2020%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQ1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=e260948c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/04/19/apple-launch-new-4-7-inch-iphone-8-2020/mobile-phone/</a><br />\n有關 Apple 將會推出 iPhone SE 2 的傳聞，已經傳出大半年，但至今還未有任何動靜。日前台灣有傳媒引述富邦證券的消息指，Apple 打算在 2020 年 3 月，發表一款更新版 iPhone 8，作為 Apple 的中階智能手機選擇。這部手機有可能稱為 iPhone 8s。<br />\n<br />\n來源：macrumors<br />\n<br />\n<br />\niPhone 8s 據說會沿用現時 iPhone 8 的機身設計，包括 4.7 吋 LCD 屏幕和單鏡頭相機。規格方面則有所更新，例如採用今年 9 月發表的 A13 處理器，並且有 128GB 儲存。現時 Apple 銷售中的中階 iPhone 只有 iPhone 7 一款，但規格已經嚴重過時，iPhone 8s 預計會取而代之，同時和小米、OPPO、vivo 等大陸品牌爭逐中階手機市場。<br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒報導指 iPhone 8s 會在明年 3 月發表，預計價格將會在 649 美元左右（約 5,090 港元）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2019/04/17/apple-launch-new-4-7-inch-iphone-8-2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macrumors.com%2F2019%2F04%2F17%2Fapple-launch-new-4-7-inch-iphone-8-2020%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQ1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=235b99bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.macrumors.com/2019/04/17/apple-launch-new-4-7-inch-iphone-8-2020/</a>"},{"pid":"ca157a992d6c22943e47762086728dfe39c24690","tid":1115694,"uid":85659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:14:50.000Z","msg":"4.7...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3dae1494944c5c1fdbb653ad368e8b6c37fd45","tid":1115694,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0